<p align="center"><font size="5"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal">Java
Virtual Classroom Teacher Tool</b><o:p>
</o:p>
</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%" align="left"><font size="4">The
purpose of the Java Teacher Tool is to provide a Java based application to the
Virtual Classroom Environment (VCE).<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>This
application is currently designated as the future extension of the Virtual
Classroom Environment with eventual integration into the Chronobot
Time-Knowledge Exchange platform.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp; </span>It
is also one hundred percent compatible with the Delphi Virtual Classroom. The
components will be dependent on the Java Virtual Machine. The version used is
Java SDK 1.5.0.<o:p>
</o:p>
</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4"><o:p>
<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal">I. Functions<o:p>
</o:p>
</b></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal">1.
Chat Features<o:p>
</o:p>
</b></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">A. Supports standard Classroom Chat
functionality<o:p>
</o:p>
</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">B. Supports Private Student-Teacher Chat
functionality<o:p>
</o:p>
</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">C. Supports chat response text speaker based
on the open source FreeTTS software platform. <o:p>
</o:p>
</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">D. Supports private chat deactivation<o:p>
</o:p>
</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">E. Supports custom emotion driven icon
representation to serve as limited visual<span style="mso-tab-count:3"> </span>communication</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4"><o:p>
<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal">2. Integrated Custom Web Browser<o:p>
</o:p>
</b></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">A. Up to four independent web browsers may
be open simultaneously in the Java Tool</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">B . Teacher may direct student learning via
Push Functionality<o:p>
</o:p>
</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">C . Student may also direct student learning
via the Push technology when given<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">&nbsp;</span>permission
to do so by the Teacher<o:p>
</o:p>
&nbsp;</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal">3.
Push Permission<o:p>
</o:p>
</b></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">A. Teacher can give/revoke web page push
permission to/from specific students or groups of students.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal">4.
Real-time Online Visual Testing<o:p>
</o:p>
</b></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">A. Teacher can import and compose timed
tests/quizzes.<o:p>
</o:p>
</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">B. Answers are displayed with icons.<o:p>
</o:p>
</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">C. Tests are automatically graded, and
results can be saved and exported.<o:p>
</o:p>
</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">D. Tests can be exported in XML format.<o:p>
</o:p>
</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4"><o:p>
<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal">5. Grade Book</b></font></p>
<p:colorscheme
 colors="#FFFFFF,#000000,#808080,#000000,#BBE0E3,#333399,#009999,#99CC00"/>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">A. Student grades can be entered into the
Grade Book.<o:p>
</o:p>
</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">B. Results of online tests are entered into
the Grade Book.<o:p>
</o:p>
</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">C. Data can be loaded and saved.<o:p>
</o:p>
</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">D. Grades can be emailed to students.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4"><b>6. Relational Index</b></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">A.&nbsp; Builds a keyword frequency file
based on VC transcripts.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">B.&nbsp; Keyword list can be manually
updated.<o:p>
</o:p>
</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4"><b>7. FaceAlive Icons</b></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">A. Allows users to individualize and
customize their emoticons.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">B. Automatically resizes any JPG image the
user selects.</font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="4">C. </font><font size="4">Fully integrated into the newest version of
Teacher Tool. </font><font size="4"><o:p>
</o:p>
</font></p>
<p align="left">&nbsp;</p>
